Resource Profile: DDCC:VS Document

Defining URL:http://worldhealthorganization.github.io/ddcc/StructureDefinition/DDCCVSDocument
Version:1.0.0
Name:DDCCVSDocument
Title:DDCC:VS Document
Status:Active as of 2022-11-23 04:25:10+0000
Definition:

A DDCC:VS Document is a document bundle containing the DDCC:VS.

Publisher:WHO
Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://worldhealthorganization.github.io/ddcc/StructureDefinition/DDCCVSDocument

bdl-4errorBundleentry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited
: entry.all(response.exists() = (%resource.type = 'batch-response' or %resource.type = 'transaction-response' or %resource.type = 'history'))

: (type = 'history') or entry.where(fullUrl.exists()).select(fullUrl&resource.meta.versionId).isDistinct()

: contained.where((('#'+id in (%resource.descendants().reference | %resource.descendants().as(canonical) | %resource.descendants().as(uri) | %resource.descendants().as(url))) or descendants().where(reference = '#').exists() or descendants().where(as(canonical) = '#').exists() or descendants().where(as(canonical) = '#').exists()).not()).trace('unmatched', id).empty()
